250,2376],", as security lovers, to a new dimension and leave the computer industry in better shape while we&lsquo;re at it.\n                  ",[2250,2376],", as security lovers, to a new dimension and leave the computer industry in better shape while we&#39;re at it.\n                  ",[2250,2376],", as security lovers, to a new dimension and leave the computer industry in better shape while we&rsquo;re at it.\n                  ",[3292,3878],"\n                    We all thrive on learning something new every day and everyone is constantly trying on different hats. We are working with new technologies while rethinking an old industry and are excited about all the possibilities and opportunities to innovate.\n                    It&apos;s a problem deeply ingrained in traditional sectors like startups and the wider service industry but which has been compounded in the past five to ten years by the emergence of the mostly tech-powered gig economy which has created a new generation of shift workers and indeed\n                  ",[3292,3878],"\n                    We all thrive on learning something new every day and everyone is constantly trying on different hats. We are working with new technologies while rethinking an old industry and are excited about all the possibilities and opportunities to innovate.\n                    It&lsquo;s a problem deeply ingrained in traditional sectors like startups and the wider service industry but which has been compounded in the past five to ten years by the emergence of the mostly tech-powered gig economy which has created a new generation of shift workers and indeed\n                  ",[3292,3878],"\n                    We all thrive on learning something new every day and everyone is constantly trying on different hats. We are working with new technologies while rethinking an old industry and are excited about all the possibilities and opportunities to innovate.\n                    It&#39;s a problem deeply ingrained in traditional sectors like startups and the wider service industry but which has been compounded in the past five to ten years by the emergence of the mostly tech-powered gig economy which has created a new generation of shift workers and indeed\n                  ",[3292,3878],"\n                    We all thrive on learning something new every day and everyone is constantly trying on different hats. We are working with new technologies while rethinking an old industry and are excited about all the possibilities and opportunities to innovate.\n                    It&rsquo;s a problem deeply ingrained in traditional sectors like startups and the wider service industry but which has been compounded in the past five to ten years by the emergence of the mostly tech-powered gig economy which has created a new generation of shift workers and indeed\n                  ",[2156,2311],"Our company is comprised of people who make bold choices for our clients and the security sector. It&apos;s in our DNA to push our limits and make bold changes.",[2156,2311],"Our company is comprised of people who make bold choices for our clients and the security sector. It&lsquo;s in our DNA to push our limits and make bold changes.",[2156,2311],"Our company is comprised of people who make bold choices for our clients and the security sector. It&#39;s in our DNA to push our limits and make bold changes.",[2156,2311],"Our company is comprised of people who make bold choices for our clients and the security sector. It&rsquo;s in our DNA to push our limits and make bold changes.",[1967,1987],"[active, autorotate, autorotateTiming, items.length]",[629,632],[629,632],[699,702],[699,702],[3732,3735],[3732,3735],[4393,4396],[4393,4396],"markAllNotificationsAsRead",[358,389],"startNotificationPolling",[389,417],[2285,2288],[2285,2288],[4775,4778],[4775,4778],[5216,5219],[5216,5219],[4928,4956],"[pathname, shouldHideHeader, switchLocale]","useI18nRouter",[522,582],"stopNotificationPolling",[898,974],